//////////////////////////////ANGULAR////////////////////////
install angular cli (to help create components) : npm install -g angular-cli
create project : ng new <project name>
go angular cli.json => outDir :'../public'
(RUN BACKEND)
(RUN FRONT)*********
cd <project name> => ng serve
***************
go into the components file => ng g component <any component>
index.html has all the shit
create router app.module.ts (approutes and imports)
refrence for templates : bittwatch/bootstrap

create forms and stuff
create service to validate inputs
imports and inject into constructor
install flash messages service ( include it fel ng modules import)
